Traffic Light Controller with 4 directions
Red, Yellow and Green LEDs are used.
Four Direction, Direction 1 and 2 in Positive logic LED Connection, 
Direction 3 and 4 in Negative logic LED Connection. G1- 30 Sec, G2- 25 Sec, G3- 15 Sec, G4- 20 Sec.

